The TRENDING page!

The cylinder and crank with compressed air supplied is not an engine. Call it a disposable air motor. Common on Co2 powered model planes in 1960's.  Buy one that is not experimental but proven reliable many years ago. Or maybe 3D print a wheel for experimentation...
